# Project 1/Benchmarks

This folder contains all the 1D benchmarks described in section 4.2 of our report.
The data for higher dimensions is found in the report.

## Content
The folders are indexed as follows:


* N - Number of particles used (number between 1 and 500)
* a - Value of variational parameter alpha used. Here, always 0.5
* IS - Optional parameter, indicating that importance sampling was used.
